{"tid":1308650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【每日一毛】連儂牆係垃圾係和理非vs拒絕勇武貼牆抗共？","createTime":"2019-07-12T02:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T04:53:23.000Z","uid":53610,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f423ffffa48c9844a2a812716313131a4e624904","tid":1308650,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:56:20.000Z","msg":"冇錯，標題兩種說法都係三毛一手包辦，神又係佢鬼又係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三毛擅長將一個議題推向兩個極端，然後再帶風向搧動兩邊人互屌，即係分化<br />\n<br />\n佢哋今日鍾意攞連儂牆嚟講，一方面開post用連儂牆洗版，另一方面又會開post屌鳩連儂牆導致運動失焦，屌人之餘都不忘加返句和理非，跟手又再開post反駁返講連儂牆幾有用再執多劑物盡其用，咁樣一個循環落嚟成個版面就成功俾佢哋佔領<br />\n<br />\n同場加映最新南亞仔事件，佢哋的處理手法係拉一捧一，一方面就南亞仔勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時會屌鳩返之前唔還手條友，以達到捧勇武踩和理的效果，跟手仲拉多條白衫友出嚟論證「和理」有幾on9，當然都唔少得要分派啲人手去屌南亞仔，加返句勇武失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目標都係嗰個，想搧動勇武和理分化，不過我相信聰明的巴絲打係唔會咁易上當，最緊要屌人之前諗真啲就得"},{"pid":"9c8b341300191c81b7da63e24071bb79c7aec4ad","tid":1308650,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:57:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3a6560656cb71886f7c6fe024a3f16a7f736e14","tid":1308650,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:58:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1a93c01ef52b588f927ea10a3eb854db86f7b3f","tid":1308650,"uid":152311,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:58:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16f29cf29f8dad456d92a160a805f3a1224fbe1f","tid":1308650,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:10:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d77da5a652e43917b6ba803c6bd58e4c6b8cb20","tid":1308650,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:12:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36576bf4525d7109d4b9f3d954a92278b1bf1276","tid":1308650,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:01:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6a978d0086703acc3a68cc1c757b6881ec732ca","tid":1308650,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:02:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1832f7209d19d8fd30ed76e2bac650e0cc0e4708","tid":1308650,"uid":30601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:03:23.000Z","msg":"互相嗌交當唱歌<br />\n之後713, 714見真章<br />\n團結群眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b9e25cf39f889aba0f6b6cb296db899f194519","tid":1308650,"uid":21887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:04:32.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<br />\n<code>我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要去醫院驗傷  我唔會解鎖電話 我唔會簽任何文件</code>"},{"pid":"27ac896667d2bea1e211483221be617b9ad080dd","tid":1308650,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:05:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66ebc84a68db66b976a978f4285917628ea10adb","tid":1308650,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8d336c1bb0e5865f0319aad84a8fb2f4c1f018b","tid":1308650,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:28:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9435ecdc970f037141e6a726396e5772febe4e7e","tid":1308650,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"推"}]}